<Body>                                                          <Title>大马644囚犯食物中毒</Title>

    <ReportTime type="absTime">2014年01月21日06:27</ReportTime> 来源：云南信息报

<Content>　　
<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Location lid="l1">马来西亚槟城监狱</Location><Participant sid="s1">超过644名囚犯</Participant><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">上周五</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="action">吃了</Denoter><Object oid="o1">狱方食物</Object></Event>
后<Event eid="e2"><Participant sid="s2">腹</Participant><Denoter did="d2" type="action">泻</Denoter>不止</Event>
，成为<Event eid="e3"><Location lid="l3">马来西亚</Location><Time tid="t3" type="timeInterval">有史以来</Time><Participant sid="s3">最多人</Participant>集体<Denoter did="d3" type="emergency">食物中毒</Denoter>的个案</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e4" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s4">马国卫生部</Participant><Denoter did="d4" type="statement">表示</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e5" polarity="negative"><Time tid="t5" type="relTime">截至昨天</Time>仍有<Participant sid="s5">50人</Participant>尚未<Denoter did="d5" type="stateChange">痊愈</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e6" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s6">卫生部主管公共卫生的副总监鲁门</Participant><Time tid="t6" type="relTime">昨天</Time>在声明中<Denoter did="d6" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e7"><Time tid="t7" type="relTime">上周五</Time>发生在<Location lid="l7">槟城监狱</Location>的集体<Denoter did="d7" type="emergency">食物中毒</Denoter>事件</Event>，共<Event eid="e8">造成<Participant sid="s8">644名囚犯</Participant><Denoter did="d8" type="action">腹泻</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence><Event eid="e9" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s9">他</Participant><Denoter did="d9" type="statement">表示</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e10"><Time tid="t10" type="relTime">截至前天上午8时</Time>，其中<Participant sid="s10">594名病患</Participant>已经<Denoter did="d10" type="stateChange">痊愈</Denoter></Event>，不过仍有<Event eid="e11"><Participant sid="s11">50人</Participant>轻微<Denoter did="d11" type="action">腹泻</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e12" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s12">他</Participant><Denoter did="d12" type="statement">说</Denoter>，这所监狱共有1233名囚犯</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>
<Event eid="e13"><Participant sid="s13">当局</Participant><Means mid="m13" type="method">调查</Means><Denoter did="d13" type="action">发现</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e14"><Time tid="t14" type="relTime">事发当天上午</Time>，<Object sid="s14">狱方提供大宝森节特餐辣椒鸡饭</Object><Denoter did="d14" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter><Object oid="o14">问题</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e15"><Object oid="o15">当天的食物</Object>是由<Participant sid="s15">四名厨师</Participant>和<Participant sid="s15">29名囚犯</Participant><Denoter did="d15" type="action">负责</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e16"><Participant sid="s16">他</Participant><Denoter did="d16" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>：“<Event eid="e17"><Object oid="o17">厨具</Object>及<Object oid="o17">食物样本</Object>都已送<Denoter did="d17" type="operation">化验</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e18"><Object sid="s18">结果</Object>最快<Time tid="t18" type="relTime">五天后</Time><Denoter did="d18" type="stateChange">出炉</Denoter></Event>。”</Sentence><Sentence>
<Event eid="e19"><Participant sid="s19">他</Participant>已<Denoter did="d19" type="statement">下令</Denoter>监狱全面消毒</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
</Content>
